modules.description: Generates type-safe SQL queries from OCaml expressions, executes them with parameter binding, and parses results into OCaml values. Works with SQL statements, query parameters, and database result sets. Enables safe and efficient interaction with SQLite databases in applications requiring structured data access.

Converts between string representations and type structures, handling input and output specifications with boolean flags. Processes SQL expression syntax to extract type information, input parameters, and output fields. Supports type mapping for database interactions and query parsing.
